As the title says, do it and enjoy the benefits.

It sounds simple, but it brings huge benefits. You get to delete all unnecessary images, free up your storage, and may save some extra money.

I don't know if you ever get into this situation, but for me, the tendency to take pictures is always greater than the tendency to review them. Whenever I see a memorable moment, I immediately pull out my phone and take a picture, but I often forget to review these pictures later on. This is the perfect opportunity to review your beautiful experiences.

That's it.

